page.title: 12WHITEHAVEN SUPERMARKETS.
page.content: Whitehaven has several supermarkets ,the newest being Presto's.It has been opened for about 6 months.It has brought employment to the area;120 jobs have been taken up by the people of Whitehaven.The most profitable sections of the store are fresh foods,fish & the bakery.The bakery is on the premises.This is an advantage because stock can be replenished when necessary.Prestos has a fresh fish dept. which no other supermarket in Whitehaven possesses.Over 4500 different articles are sold in the shop & nearly every country in the world supplies goods.Another good seller is the items in the wine,beer & spirits dept.Customers say this branch is more expensive than the one in Workington but the management disagree.An inexpensive car park nearby helps to attract customers.
